&lt;li&gt;Contact patients regarding upcoming appointments and follow-up needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with patient re-engagement efforts for individuals who have become difficult to reach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document all patient interactions and outreach attempts according to program standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support patient retention efforts by identifying and addressing barriers to engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
